metadata.name: The Fog
metadata.description:
I love chasing weather and storms, fog is one of my favorites.

This is the story of a city gripped with fog and unexplained phenomenon.

The year is 2022, the city is Toronto...  
There are rumors and urban legends that creatures lurk within the fog..  
The fog has been showing up everyday and is so dense that even with a flashlight you couldn't see 2 feet in front of you. 
I have been documenting and investigating the fog occurrences to see if they are linked to the missing people in the city.

As I start my day I brew a fresh cup of coffee, grab my gear, my camera, my protection and I head to the roof which is the first stop.
